dc_title_s: Map Showing Lands Under Tidewater of Delaware River at Camden, N.J. Inshore of Pierhead Line to be Occupied by Bridge of Delaware River Bridge Joint Commission
dc_description_s: Delaware River to Front Street between Penn Street and Elm Street in Camden. Map shows the pierhead and bulkhead lines adopted by the Board of Commerce and Navigation on September 21, 1916. Also shows the lands granted, limits of bridge, and lands for which damages are claimed.
